channel.title: If you help a admins. will be hired for my new sever...but i need help
channel.description:
Unrealscape!! Its going good...its very fun so far ive tested 10 times and i think its know good :D. But...im stuck..first off i can make it but i need to know how to make ip for exp. Unrealscape.no-ip.info or Unrealscaoe.no-ip.org. Also I need to Someone to help me or tell me How do i f.. get the lava cape and fury good items on game good for morpascape...cuz when i wear them using ::pickup 0312 1 or sothiong it freezes when i wear and last question tell me were we should respawn..anywere u choose! I was thinking temple were u get the dessuart tressure magicks. Heres some things i made into a game and its a very..first time..
Unrealscape! No using the stupied haimcia things whatever it is :D The duel arena is were you can pk or fight whatever one you like most. The Widly is were the 3 gods are and they fight only at back at lvl 56 widly..U see all mages of anykind of god fight eachother and kill them get the cape and staff...Widly u can not kill there.. The ruins of the old place near the end of the widly like lvl 49 Greatdemon place..Go there and kill the barrows and kill like 2 torghs get 1 barrow item. The rares are at the varrock at the entrance of castle front.. In middle staff shop has all the staff u could think of. The clothing shops has all kinds of capes gloves..and other stuff..The gloves of barrows are not at that shop.. gernal store has pots, food,runes, and... The werid item i found.. and i put it in there hit pull and it sends you to the daggys king at same respawn..the island. Im still working on the Death..how we get mods to glow..and admins..
Before i end this post... If you answer one of my questions or so... The spot for admins. is yours! Free @#$% for everyone!!!
